oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and brown on white) announcing the Hank Williams Memorial Concert and Festival of Music with Jett Williams and The Drifting Cowboys, and George Hamilton IV at the Fayette County Memorial Building on June 25. Poster features metal photoplates of Jett Williams, The Drifting Cowboys, and George Hamilton IV.
